Class DiffusionParameters

Namespace
Vts.Modeling.ForwardSolvers
Assembly
Vts.dll

This class allows creation and copying of a diffusion parameters object, which contains fields necessary for solution of diffusion models. The creation is made by passing an OpticalProperties object.
